seo.pageDescription: Request Early Access to MetaMask Institutional

node.headline: Request Early Access to MetaMask Institutional

childMarkdownRemark.html:
On May 8th, Fireblocks, the #1 digital asset management platform, will launch its partnership with MetaMask Institutional (MMI), the leading web3 wallet for organizations. We will grant 25 companies early access to the integration.

With this integration, you get the best in blockchain security and key management alongside unrivaled access to web3.

MMI supplements the Fireblocks web3 experience with the following:

Access to 17,000+ web3 dapps and protocols.
Enhanced web3 portfolio management with powerful institutional controls, digital asset monitoring, and in-depth transaction reporting—all on one dashboard.
Team management settings with automated onboarding, and organization-wide portfolio views.
Performance and P&L attribution metrics for all ERC-20 tokens and the largest DeFi protocols
Versatile web3 access through the MMI browser extension, portfolio dashboard, and API.

One wallet. All of web3.
